get_tcom_adsl_pass - Enter user/pass, get your router's current IP. If you don't want to run DynDNS or something similar
Author: Tonimir Kisasondi


usage:

$ python tcomgetip.py your_username


or, simply import tcomgetip and call:
get_tcom_adsl_ip(user,passwd)

that's it...

Depends on requests, since i'm lazy to use urllib2
